title: Eight Hundred Hokage - Novel Updates
author: 聊天群
description:
“Minato Namikaze (Anbu) is about to wake up, pay attention to check.”

“Tsunade, did you take my money again!”

The 2 years old Tsunade was dumbfounded, this money, isn’t it for her own use?

On the other side, the 90 years old Hashirama wanted to come over to help his granddaughter to say a few good words, but when he just moved, he flashed to his waist.

“Oni-chan, you just be careful.” The 8 years old Tobirama, said so.>
